<p>Hello <%= @resource.name %>!</p>

<p>Someone has requested a link to change your password. You can do this through the link below.</p>

<%= link_to "Change my password", edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token, host: @host), class: "btn btn-primary p-3 fw-700 ax-center" %>

<p class="text-muted">If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
<p class="text-muted">Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.</p>
